cc:Work.dc:title: FlexBook
cc:Work.dc:description:
Box with living hinge styled after a book.
If you have an enclosure, arrange the living hinge to be as close to your extractor fan as possible.
![Open](static/samples/FlexBook-2.jpg)
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes FlexBook --FingerJoint_angle=90.0 --FingerJoint_style=rectangular --FingerJoint_surroundingspaces=2.0
